{"tid":1850243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔應該良心價賣口罩","createTime":"2020-01-29T12:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T12:30:49.000Z","uid":310487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6d53f633884c2c6507be99a7692cc4fbfa290acd","tid":1850243,"uid":310487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:22:22.000Z","msg":"今日見到有幾條片講藍屍廢老搶唔到平價口罩發爛渣，真係良心當狗肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衰啲講句真係唔想賣比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過如果想賣口罩，又唔想比人鬧，又想幫到人，會唔會考慮下跟返藥房價賣，然後將賺多左既收入捐出?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我咁提議因為以下原因<br />\n1. 而家需求 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; 供應，就算你拎幾多貨出黎，應該都滿足唔到所有人，反而會比人鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 平價賣只係將買家既成本由錢變成時間，逼人排隊，排排下有武肺混入去既話...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 抽籤/排隊或各種分流方法都未必可以將口罩賣比有需要既人，因為會有插隊/炒賣黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 只有提高價錢，先可以將需求量(quantity demanded)降低，唔洗排幾個蛇餅然後又買唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 要提高價錢，但又唔係賺國難財，其中一個方法就係捐左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6. 口罩基本上實賣得出，只要有貨既話你捐定先都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9dcfd52e60d6141737facde4376c0e47a7371c","tid":1850243,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:23:34.000Z","msg":"[狼人] 武漢肺炎大逃殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f2ad2356da44f75723be5751cce9e2340ccf5e65","tid":1850243,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:30:49.000Z","msg":"正視聽！僱主有責任為僱員提供口罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1850226/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1850226/page/1</a>"}]}